b382f311-5f40-4c07-9545-5326c1426bc7.title: <player>
b382f311-5f40-4c07-9545-5326c1426bc7.text: What can you do to help a bold adventurer like myself?

options.text: What can you do to help a bold adventurer like myself?

f928cc3f-4e8b-4683-94d2-d3be4f63c7f6.title: Brother Jered
f928cc3f-4e8b-4683-94d2-d3be4f63c7f6.text:
Well if you put a string on that holy symbol I can
bless it for you or I could tell you about skillcapes.

f12eada2-03d6-4fc3-b662-3f52e8a876d8.title: Brother Jered
f12eada2-03d6-4fc3-b662-3f52e8a876d8.text: Yes! Praise he who brings life to this world.

options.text: Tell me about the Skillcape of Prayer.

8e8c022e-c262-42b1-b6b8-c7563b04b8fa.text:
You give Jered the symbol. Jered closes his eyes
and places his hand on the symbol. He softly chants. Jered
passes you the holy symbol.

options.text: Tell me about the Skillcape of Prayer.

2289eb95-8a20-4ad3-b5cf-e6735adc8bd1.title: Brother Jered
2289eb95-8a20-4ad3-b5cf-e6735adc8bd1.text:
If you have a silver star, which is the holy symbol of
Saradomin, then I can bless it. Then if you are
wearing it, it will help you when you are praying.

85e199e7-4d3b-43bf-95c6-1ddeb34b2efc.title: <player>
85e199e7-4d3b-43bf-95c6-1ddeb34b2efc.text: Tell me about the Skillcape of Prayer.

67dd861b-6f70-437e-bfa2-0d660a0c91b8.title: Brother Jered
67dd861b-6f70-437e-bfa2-0d660a0c91b8.text:
The Skillcape of Prayer is the hardest of all the
skillcapes to get, it requires much devotion to acquire
but also imbues the wearer with the ability to briefly fly!

36935d54-ae2b-49f0-b47a-c3cf2d45d506.title: Brother Jered
36935d54-ae2b-49f0-b47a-c3cf2d45d506.text:
The Cape of Prayer also increases the amount of
Prayer points restored from drinking potions when it is
equipped. Is there something else I can do for you?
